<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-17 01:40 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9461 &Cx1f; tth-z
u s BC-BKC-VECSEY-COLUMN-SPI     03-17 0953
