<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-17 13:23 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9730 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u s BC-OUTDOORS-COLUMN-BOS &LR;      03-17 0945
