A0402 &Cx1f; taf-z
u a BC-BROWN-SHOOTING-1STLD-     03-17 0993
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-BROWN-SHOOTING-1STLD-WRITETHRU-ART-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
FORMER ACTIVIST H. RAP BROWN SOUGHT FOR SHOOTING OFFICERS IN
ATLANTA 
</HEADLINE>
   (subs for rewriting, updating and more detail throughout; story
grows by about 300 words)  
