<P>
   These are the stories The San Francisco Chronicle Business
section plans to move for Friday, March 17, on the New York Times
wire. For questions, please call Greg Ambrose at 415-777-7219 or
the business desk at 415-536-5172. For business stories running in
main news, call the news desk at 415-777-7074.
</P>
