Dallas Museum of Art, surveys a dozen artists who used photography
to further their art. Pierre Bonnard took the photograph at left,
``Martha Bathing,'' (Musee d'Orsay/The New York Times) and used it
for his oil at right, ``Nu au Tub.'' (Musee National d'Art
Moderne/The New York Times) LITE
