which has not been seen here since 1995, The Alfisti, as Alfa
enthusiasts are known, would love to see these cars come to the
United States. ``There is definitely an opening for entry-level
Italian sports cars here,'' said Vic Cerami, chapter president of
the Long Island Alfa Romeo Owners Club. (The New York Times)
