<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-17 23:25 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0682 &Cx1f; taf-z
u s BC-BKC-NCAA-SOUTH-NYT &LR;      03-17 0650
